{"tid":1565952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「正視聽」願榮光歸香港是神曲！香港人民族情緒前所未有咁高漲！","createTime":"2019-09-13T10:53:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T20:34:24.000Z","uid":167548,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9a3eb15c921705252c55a8426abf8ee1e5174b2b","tid":1565952,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:53:36.000Z","msg":"但是你唔可以首歌會令人有疲態想開開心心去唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n我見到好多討論PO都是被狙擊分化或者敵人反對我要做嘅心態終結討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家聽我一言，呢首歌是一定要唱。去商場唱會唔會有反效果? 和理非會唔會日後淨是去商場唱，星期日有risk就唔去。你要明白好多和理非會覺得參加一個半個活動就當出左力。<br />\n<br />\n一句到尾9.15個日正式第一次星期日版嘅非法集結！呢日好撚重要，上次831就是星期六得幾十萬人。<br />\n<br />\n9.15 東角道見<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n百萬人匯師銅鑼灣！<br />\n呢次真是第一次星期日港島版非法集結！<br />\n我真是希望首歌有用，凝聚到百萬人堅持上街！"},{"pid":"6f54df52e49c5e60aab7526019ed14ed3ded0bf1","tid":1565952,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:54:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=73051847\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各區集合地點!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n油麻地、佐敦、尖沙咀: 梳士巴利公園(太空館附近)<br />\n荃灣、大窩口、青衣: 荃灣公園(海濱長廊)、青衣海濱長廊<br />\n葵興、葵芳、荔景: 林士德遊樂場、葵涌運動場<br />\n美孚: 嶺南之風<br />\n太子、旺角: 花墟公園<br />\n荔枝角、長沙灣: 長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗: 通州街公園<br />\n油塘、藍田: 油塘道遊樂場<br />\n將軍澳、寶琳、坑口、康城<br />\n中西區（西區、中環、金鐘、半山、山頂）<br />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"3557a23d778316ea0f764b7883107df6f5a4c7be","tid":1565952,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:56:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67ac0d0efb2803b5435ae1d4eb63bbd5d40567b1","tid":1565952,"uid":170297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:57:37.000Z","msg":"9.15 東角道見"},{"pid":"76ee1f8702c3405245bc0ad3d92db7a1ab3a595e","tid":1565952,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:57:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c8f41d5925fdfa81ff1a628aff2757d1745f4f0","tid":1565952,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:58:41.000Z","msg":"唔好再打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab87c13b879644aa5d199025922d507b752d6ed4","tid":1565952,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:01:02.000Z","msg":"915"},{"pid":"8b1a87820b9a7ff47f06b435685bb71171fc9787","tid":1565952,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:01:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff8554be7ab7c59e6d9d27a2408d015e1bd4d0e4","tid":1565952,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:02:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3372c7d0ce890ea3ae1417b6a4cce13230ecdc4b","tid":1565952,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:04:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5090ab8759415c42b564702f494c3f8016838e6","tid":1565952,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:05:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5227e7706d095e627ee296eaf5ea1fe18bfc023","tid":1565952,"uid":41608,"